                        </div>
                        <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="order_question_3" style="height: 0px;">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>
                                    If an item is out of stock the Bargain.pk Customer Service Team will notify you as soon as possible. For regular stock items, you can either get a replacement item or wait for an item to get in the stock. For discontinued items, you can get a replacement item or cancel your order.
