                            <h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#order_question_6" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" class="accordion-toggle collapsed">I tried to check out and the item in my shopping cart disappeared, what happened?<i class="fa fa-caret-down"></i></a></h4>
