                                <p>
                                    Note
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Some Items may not be available for CoD</li>
                                        <li>The maximum order value for CoD is 100,000 PKR</li>
                                        <li>Gift cards or vouchers cannot be used to make CoD payments</li>
                                     </ol>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
