                                <p>Different items have different return policies. </p>
                                <p>Any open box/container of supplements and healthcare items are not eligible for either return or exchange. If the box or container is unsealed and you are not 100% satisfied with your purchase from Bargain you can return your item(s) for  an exchange or refund within 30 days of purchase. </p>
